Interface IStatementContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BOp, Cloneable, IGroupMemberNode, IPropertySet, IQueryNode, IVariableBindingRequirements, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConstructNode, QuadData, StatementPatternNode

    public interface IStatementContainer
extends IGroupMemberNode
    Marker interface for things which either are statements (or statement patterns) or contain statements (or statement pattern). This is used to create an abstraction for QuadData from which we can then specialize the ConstructNode
